  <brief_title>Clinical Study for the Impact of Bio-absorbable Felt (NEOVEIL®) With Fibrin Sealant on Removal of Drainage Tube After Minimally Invasive Gastrectomy for Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Study for the Impact of Bio-absorbable Felt (NEOVEIL®) With Fibrin Sealant on Removal of Drainage Tube After Minimally Invasive Gastrectomy for Gastric Cancer: Multicenter Prospective Randomized Comparison Study</official_title>
